"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b9caab6183812c9be9ccade7ff5cb9232f73c5","tid":2290462,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"話說在70年代屯門要發展為新市鎮，政府要在青山灣填海興建三聖邨，並擴建青山公路，自然要炸開這塊巨石。當時準備炸石的前一晚，全部工人都突然染上怪病。其後每次炸石時，工人都會出意外或者生病。眾人都生怕會惹怒靈石，不敢動工。<br />\n<br />\n之後由另一間公司接手，怪事又再發生。首次炸石時，巨石竟然絲毫無損，石隙更流出紅色液體。街坊認為巨石有靈氣，可說是麒麟崗鎮山之石，而且被對面玉鼠島的鼠精依附，能夠保佑當地居民。最後經過商討，政府同意把青山公路繞過巨石，更把巨石劃為地界，並立下石碑。<br />\n<br />\n都市傳說通常不止一個版本，另一個版本接續上面的傳說，流傳指當時新界民政署的洋人高官認為是無稽之談，堅持要炸石。豈料籌備炸石之前，項目的工程師卻死於非命，湊巧這名工程師就是高官的兒子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190714/IY3CLYFVJ5A7MEPAQ5HXGNB44A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190714%2FIY3CLYFVJ5A7MEPAQ5HXGNB44A%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1RSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=592a0119\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190714%2FIY3CLYFVJ5A7MEPAQ5HXGNB44A%2F&h=c67a0049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190714/IY3CLYFVJ5A7MEPAQ5HXGNB44A/</a>"},{"pid":"3ef968560e633ff244f9f0aa0177cd7b9feee321","tid":2290462,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4078c0bd8b228d93c21b60167310ea1b9698420d","tid":2290462,"uid":151074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"食環搗破&hellip;聽到都覺得on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:25:01.000Z","msg":"入面先人聽著，你地已經被重重包圍啦，立即舉高雙手，慢慢行出黎投降"},{"pid":"cf28feccd2c50065dabb7cf625bd1dbb4733b9b7","tid":229